Program: Outlook
Title: The Murder of Lucy Blackman
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03kbrz5
Last Broadcast Date: Not available
Tim Blackman talks about his impact statement after the murder of his daughter Lucy Blackman. Also, Hossein Derakhshan's weblog about Iran. Rockaradio and it's aim to bridge the divide between British traveller and settled communities. Finally, an interview with Kenyan singer Nyota Ndogo (Little Star). Presenter: Frederick Dove Show less